|herman ( peter noone ) in a dutch dairy factory , after the handing over of a gold record for no milk today in the netherlands ( 1966 ) peter blair denis bernard noone ( born 5 november 1947 ) is an english singer - songwriter , guitarist , pianist and actor , best known as herman of the successful 1960s pop group herman 's hermits .

